messages.messageBody:
Julian has been going crazy with his guitar lately and last night he decided
to stay up late and play.

This morning he announced he wrote a song. It's REALLY good, with guitar
chords and everything... we were very impressed.

Hey, for folks going to SC -- Julian is planning to bring his Magic cards,
and would love others interested to do so as well.

Kathryn
